description:
“The truth is… I am Iron Man.” Tony Stark put down his Mobile and looked at the press in front of him with a serious face, but his heart was screaming. What’s wrong with being an arms dealer?

System, why do I have to admit my identity?!  Beep.. when Tony’s Arc reactor in his chest warned. “Sorry, my daughter is calling me. He accidentally crossed the world of Iron and turned into an Iron Man with a twist.”>
